{"sequence":24,"timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:27:03.664156032Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-1-ca61896e","body":"`src/shared/domain.rs:270-277` introduces a reusable `BackendRole::to_policy_role()` helper, but `BackendRole::CompletionJudge` is also what `BackendRole::for_stage(StageId::FinalReview)` returns while `stage_to_policy_role(StageId::FinalReview)` still maps to `BackendPolicyRole::FinalReviewer` (`src/contexts/agent_execution/policy.rs:423-425`). `AgentExecutionService::timeout_for_role()` now delegates through that new helper (`src/contexts/agent_execution/service.rs:178-183`), so any future caller that reuses it for final-review work will silently pick completer timeouts instead of final-review timeouts. Keep this mapping local to requirements, or make the conversion stage/context-aware instead of exposing a misleading global mapping.","dedup_key":"e927b8b8adf44647e97e9ee1b44e8bdaa3cc134daa6f5c407371c0120c68688f","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260422054431","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":25,"timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:27:03.688218102Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-1-5c50c7ee","body":"`src/contexts/automation_runtime/daemon_loop.rs:5088-5095` and `src/contexts/conformance_spec/scenarios.rs:159-172,295-304` still construct `RequirementsService` from an `EffectiveConfig` without calling `AgentExecutionService::with_effective_config(...)`. After this branch, those builders no longer match production timeout behavior: requirements invocations created through them ignore configured `backends.<family>.timeout_seconds` / `role_timeouts.*` and fall back to the default timeout. Update these helper builders to attach the same `effective_config` clone as the production builder so daemon/conformance regressions can actually exercise the configured-timeout path.","dedup_key":"6926da67a7e6321f47bcebe2083ab70f816f8d690824780b265fc84eac63b4f5","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260422054431","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
